<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-14T00:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-09-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="574" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d574">
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>Following their fourth meeting the Foreign Ministers temporarily
                                adjourned until Monday, September 18, in order to participate in the
                                fifth session of the <gloss target="#t_NATO1">NATO</gloss> Council.
                                For documentation on the Council meetings, see <ref target="#pg_85">pages 85</ref> ff.</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>